data.title: Brevard County Government
data.meta_description: Official website for Brevard County, Florida government.
data.text:
Advisory Boards

View a list of Brevard County advisory boards, members, vacancies and apply to become a member. Meeting minutes and agendas are available for download.

County Jobs

Explore job openings with Brevard County Government and start on your career path to success.

Pay Utility Services

Online account access and payment for Mims, Barefoot Bay and San Sebastian Woods water and sewer bills.

Building Permits

View records related to Code Enforcement and Contractor Licensing cases. This provides immediate access to record information.

Find a Licensed Contractor

Search for licensed contractors by license number, business name, contractor last name or contractor trade.

Fire Rescue Sponsorship Program

Interested in sponsorship to become a Brevard County Fire Rescue Firefighter or Emergency Medical Technician? Submit an Interest Card to get started.
